---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Newsletter from '../components/Newsletter.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now"
  description={`What I am working on right now at ${SITE.name}.`}
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" role="main" class="container fade-in">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>NOW</h1>
      <p>
        This is a /now page, inspired by <a href="https://sive.rs/now" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Derek Sivers</a>. While an "About" page tells you about my past, this page focuses on <strong>what I am doing right now</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>Current Theme Features</h2>
      <p>
        SignalPaper is steadily evolving. We have currently implemented the following core features and experience designs:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Premium Typography</strong>: Carefully tuned sans-serif fonts for English and system-level Chinese fonts, ensuring comfortable long-form reading.</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Floating TOC</strong>: Automatically extracts H2/H3 headings, displayed on the right side with scroll-tracking highlight. Gracefully hides on smaller screens or when there are no headings.</li>
        <li><strong>Multi-dimensional Content</strong>: Separation of <code>Posts</code> and <code>Projects</code>. Projects support lifecycle status tracking (Idea / Active / Shipped, etc.).</li>
        <li><strong>Native Bilingual Support</strong>: Built-in global English/Chinese toggle, independent URL routing, and multilingual SEO optimization.</li>
        <li><strong>Geeky Search Experience</strong>: <code>⌘K</code> shortcut support with fast local full-text browser search.</li>
        <li><strong>Polished UI Details</strong>: Seamless dark/light mode toggle, immersive image zooming (Medium Zoom), and one-click code copying.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Development Roadmap</h2>
      <p>
        Independent development is an iterative process. Here is what I plan to add to SignalPaper in the future:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Webmention Integration</strong>: Integrate likes, reposts, and comments from social networks.</li>
        <li><strong>Timeline / Changelog View</strong>: A timeline component suitable for quick thoughts or project updates.</li>
        <li><strong>Statistics Dashboard</strong>: Intuitively display personal output data (word counts, tag heatmaps, etc.).</li>
        <li><strong>Automated Workflows</strong>: Provide better scripts for one-click publishing from Obsidian or Notion to Astro.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <em>Last updated: May 2026</em>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider-wrap">
      <hr class="section-divider" />
    </div>

    <section class="newsletter-section">
      <Newsletter />
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-20);
  }
  .prose h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
  }
  .divider-wrap {
    margin: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-8) 0;
  }
  .section-divider {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }
</style>
